  "notes": "Flowmap (relational) A/B variant of the OD-flows applet. Same upstream pipeline as docs/story_data/flows (silver bucketing, per-(origen,destino) viajes aggregation with a 24h pivot, windowed-sum / day_count divisor, top-N=8000 deterministic tie-break, distrito-centroid anchoring) \u2014 only the output shape differs. locations.json = [{id,lon,lat}] for every referenced distrito (no name column in the source geojson). Each <window>_<daytype>.json = [{origin,dest,count,hourly[24]}] where count is trips/day and hourly[h] is that hour's trips/day (Sum(hourly)~=count); scrub hour h by setting count=hourly[h]. month-window comparison, NOT a climate average; 3 months on disk (Feb/May/Jun)."
